\id PHM
\h FILEMON
\toc1 Filemon
\toc2 Filemon
\toc3 Filemon
\mt1 Filemon
\c 1
\s1 Pol Nẽ Aanya
\p 
\v 1 Aya, Pol, Kristus Jesus nẽ kalabus tamo, neda turada Timoti ado,
\p oboida ado kabĩ turada Filemon gein,
\v 2 mainada Afia, kusĩ tamo turada Akipus ado, sios ogon fõ bun guru difedig gein pas enei matotof.
\p 
\v 3 Wau ifenẽya ado wau inosiya, Negur neda Tamada ado Odug Jesus Kristus bunem õ bun ibodõf.
\s1 De Fiyẽya Ado Kosẽya
\p 
\v 4 Aya, neu kosẽ bun, õ nigin karĩ aul fen, neu Negur faimud de afiyẽdig,
\v 5 ere nigin, aya, ogon momoiya Odug Jesus bun ilen anĩ karĩ au fen, Negur nẽ tamo kayau ganan nigin ogon waũ laa fiya anĩ karĩ audig.
\v 6 Aya, õ amã geid ogon momoiya nẽ uyu kũ fiya anĩ kabĩ yale di, ereb ereb biya ganan, Kristus bun ada talef anĩ, õ kisi feleya bagai keleĩ youf nigin kosẽ auf.
\v 7 Ogon waũ laa fiya anim, wau al fiya odug ifana fen, neu wau yalesen, ere nigin, turau õ, Negur nẽ tamo kayau neid waud filolõ fiya wenẽdin.
\s1 Pol Onesimus Nigin To Fen
\p 
\v 8 Anĩ nigin, Kristus bunem aya sã megeir afar fen, õ arokonõ di, ereb õ agouf nigin kisi feleya,
\v 9 anĩ ere, aya wau laa fiya bun afar fen, totol bagai to ayok. Aya, Pol, tamo tubau fen, gama Kristus Jesus nẽ kalabus tamo,
\v 10 aya neu kesu Onesimus nigin totol bagai to ayok, ĩ kokolin afar mog, neu kesu wõ yen.
\v 11 Kulu ĩ õ nigin to biyan, anĩ ere, gama ĩ ada uruwom nigin biya bagai.
\p 
\v 12 Aya, ĩ, õ gein kel sur afef, ĩ aya neu oboiyou.
\v 13 Aya ĩ uruwom mabodom are, sain aya biya od nigin kokolin afar mog, ĩ ogon modoũ yale fen, isennam.
\v 14 Anĩ ere, aya õ waũ to irõ mog, aya ereb taka naig be fiya age afouf nigin to oroun, are õ nugo yõya bunem sã, ogon oroya dõ wo agouf nigin age afen.
\v 15 Momoi, ĩ õ uruwom sain naal bagai fara gen nẽ gariya are, õ ĩ baban gai gai kel walouf nigin be,
\v 16 ĩ baban ferfer gen sã, anĩ ere, ferfer wal fiya, turã bagai. Ĩ aya bun neu oboiyou, anĩ ere, ĩ õ bun ogon oboi bagai neu wal fiya, are tamo nẽ lo fiya bun ado Odug nẽ lo fiya bun age fiyauf.
\p 
\v 17 Anĩ nigin, õ, aya ogon kabĩ turã gen ago kisi wouf are, aya aan wiyaf gen, ĩg ago aan wiyẽf.
\v 18 Ĩ õ bun ereb sane taka age fen be, ereb wareg taka adouf, wareg are aya bun uno.
\v 19 Aya, Pol, imaum bagai enei atotof. Aya fau aba afonõf, aya, õ aya bun ogon mata nigin wareg ado anĩ nigin õ to arokonok.
\v 20 Turau, aya fau õ bun tamal, ereb biya Odug bun alouf nigin orouf, Kristus bun, aya wau filolõ fiya wana.
\v 21 Ogon dõ fiya anĩ momoi auf nigin, aya atotkonok, aya to ayok anĩ wal fiya agouf anĩ aya keleĩ.
\p 
\v 22 Agef fen takag yeir. Aab taka, aya nigin dodok wana, ere nigin, ãgenei kosẽya bunem, aya baban ã bun kelau asi, an abodõf nigin, aya wau isef.
\p 
\v 23 Epafras, Kristus Jesus bun neu kalabus turau, õ bun aanya sur fef.
\v 24 Mak, Aristakus, Demas ado, Luk, neu kabĩ turau tar idig age difef.
\p 
\v 25 Odug Jesus Kristus nẽ wau ifenẽya ãgenei uur bun ibodõf. 
